me go back to sleep!

34
00:03:25,650 --> 00:03:28,275
[AYAKO] Did you have a
bad dream or something?

35
00:03:32,567 --> 00:03:36,775
[NARIHISAGO] When I piloted the
bogus Mizuhanome in the id well,

36
00:03:36,858 --> 00:03:39,858
this must've been the
world it constructed.

37
00:03:39,942 --> 00:03:42,442
That's why it's different
from what I usually find

38
00:03:42,525 --> 00:03:45,317
when I dive into a well.

39
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:48,150
There's no Kaeru,
and this place,

40
00:03:48,233 --> 00:03:51,567
it's an undistorted
version of the past.

41
00:03:51,650 --> 00:03:54,358
Could ya do me a favor
and stop staring at me?

42
00:03:54,442 --> 00:03:55,608
