loves you, sweetheart.

44
00:03:58,317 --> 00:04:01,525
Now stop being a little drama
queen and finish your breakfast.

45
00:04:01,608 --> 00:04:03,067
[MUKU]
Fine.

46
00:04:03,150 --> 00:04:06,692
[NARIHISAGO] For some reason,
I retained my memory.

47
00:04:06,775 --> 00:04:10,317
I'm not some brilliant
detective. Just me.

48
00:04:14,108 --> 00:04:17,442
Yeah, they found the body of
some person beaten to death.

49
00:04:17,525 --> 00:04:20,317
