you've been working on.

50
00:04:23,275 --> 00:04:26,775
[NARIHISAGO] In this reality,
my family's still alive.

51
00:04:26,858 --> 00:04:30,400
I've got no idea how long this
time with them is gonna last,

52
00:04:30,483 --> 00:04:34,483
but if this is the past,
I have an advantage.

53
00:04:34,567 --> 00:04:37,608
I remember everything.

54
00:04:37,692 --> 00:04:40,442
