55
00:04:40,525 --> 00:04:41,942
[INVESTIGATOR A]
Tests on chemical traces

56
00:04:42,025 --> 00:04:43,817
found on the body
came back positive

57
00:04:43,900 --> 00:04:46,067
as a finish used
in boxing gloves,

58
00:04:46,150 --> 00:04:48,983
or other similar protective
athletic hand gear.

59
00:04:49,067 --> 00:04:52,775
