tissue, vomit and diarrhea,

60
00:04:52,858 --> 00:04:54,025
vitreous humor
from prior victims--

61
00:04:54,108 --> 00:04:55,358
[DIRECTOR]
Shut that door!

62
00:04:55,442 --> 00:04:57,567
Take a seat or leave.

63
00:05:02,525 --> 00:05:03,775
