to see you, Momoki.

68
00:05:17,858 --> 00:05:20,483
Then why haven't you
been answering my calls?

69
00:05:20,567 --> 00:05:22,775
[NARIHISAGO] Just didn't
wanna get you involved.

70
00:05:22,858 --> 00:05:26,108
What do you mean by "involved"?
What're you up to now?

71
00:05:26,192 --> 00:05:28,817
[NARIHISAGO] Something with
no effect on reality.

72
00:05:28,900 --> 00:05:30,942
Could you be more specific?

73
00:05:33,775 --> 00:05:34,858
[MOMOKI]
Where are we?

74
00:05:34,942 --> 00:05:37,108
Denshin Katsuyama's house.

75
00:05:37,192 --> 00:05:38,483
Or should I say,

76
00:05:38,567 --> 00:05:40,400
it's the home of the killer
we call the Challenger.

77
00:05:40,483 --> 00:05:41,608
What?

78
00:05:41,692 --> 00:05:42,900
I need you to go to
the rear of the house

79
00:05:42,983 --> 00:05:44,608
and wait for my signal.

80
00:05:44,692 --> 00:05:47,442
Don't walk away!
Do you have any evidence?

81
00:05:47,525 --> 00:05:49,692
[NARIHISAGO]
I've been here before.

82
00:05:51,358 --> 00:05:53,483
[doorbell rings]

83
00:05:53,567 --> 00:05:54,692
[CHALLENGER]
Yes?

84
00:05:54,775 --> 00:05:57,150
[NARIHISAGO]
Good morning to you.

85
00:05:57,233 --> 00:05:58,400
[CHALLENGER]
Who're you?

86
00:05:58,483 --> 00:06:01,275
Mister Katsuyama,
I mean, Mister Challenger.

87
00:06:01,358 --> 00:06:05,692
Well, I'm a police officer and
I would like to speak with you.

88
00:06:05,775 --> 00:06:08,733
Just one-on-one.

89
00:06:08,817 --> 00:06:10,150
[CHALLENGER]
Enter.

90
00:06:15,608 --> 00:06:17,483
[NARIHISAGO]
Thanks for your cooperation.

91
00:06:17,567 --> 00:06:19,442
I hope I'm not disturbing you.

92
00:06:19,525 --> 00:06:20,608
[CHALLENGER]
Of course not.

93
00:06:20,692 --> 00:06:23,317
Now, what business
might you and I have?

94
00:06:23,400 --> 00:06:25,942
It doesn't appear friendly.

95
00:06:26,025 --> 00:06:28,775
Yeah, last time I was
racing the SWAT team,

96
00:06:28,858 --> 00:06:31,483
so I had to come
in guns blazing.

97
00:06:31,567 --> 00:06:34,900
Thought I'd take the
liberty of a redo.

98
00:06:34,983 --> 00:06:36,358
We're lucky.

99
00:06:36,442 --> 00:06:39,692
We can take our time,
and not have to rush.

100
00:06:39,775 --> 00:06:42,608
In short, I'm here to
challenge the Challenger

101
00:06:42,692 --> 00:06:44,942
