fight, like a man.

102
00:06:45,025 --> 00:06:46,192
[CHALLENGER]
Hmm.

103
00:06:46,275 --> 00:06:49,817
We've never met. What do
you mean by "last time"?

104
00:06:49,900 --> 00:06:53,483
As for "lucky," I'm not sure
I would agree with you.

105
00:06:53,567 --> 00:06:56,942
[NARIHISAGO] What I'm saying is,
this time, we'll do it your way.

106
00:06:57,025 --> 00:07:01,817
I'm assuming by "my way,"
you mean this? Correct?

107
00:07:01,900 --> 00:07:04,983
Here or inside that little
basement arena you've got,

108
00:07:05,067 --> 00:07:06,900
wherever you prefer.

109
00:07:08,067 --> 00:07:11,108
