currently occupied.

110
00:07:17,275 --> 00:07:20,525
[NARIHISAGO] How's this work?
You bang a gong?

111
00:07:20,608 --> 00:07:23,150
True combat only begins
the moment both fighters

112
00:07:23,233 --> 00:07:25,108
acknowledge it's inevitable.

113
00:07:25,192 --> 00:07:27,442
[NARIHISAGO]
Heh. "Combat."

114
00:07:27,525 --> 00:07:31,817
