What you are is
a fucking pervert

116
00:07:33,483 --> 00:07:36,650
who got off by beating a
14-year-old girl to death.

117
00:07:36,733 --> 00:07:37,817
[CHALLENGER]
Hm.

118
00:07:37,900 --> 00:07:40,900
