am fairly strong.

123
00:07:52,775 --> 00:07:56,067
[NARIHISAGO] Save it until
after you defeat an adult.

124
00:07:56,150 --> 00:07:58,817
Oh, but I have.

125
00:07:58,900 --> 00:08:00,358
[NARIHISAGO]
Oh, that's right.

126
00:08:00,442 --> 00:08:04,150
