and a martial artist.

127
00:08:04,233 --> 00:08:05,275
So what?

128
00:08:05,358 --> 00:08:06,650
A guy who gets off
on beating the shit

129
00:08:06,733 --> 00:08:07,775
outta women and children

130
00:08:07,858 --> 00:08:10,733
is the weakest kinda
scumbag there is!

131
00:08:13,442 --> 00:08:16,733
Seriously, are you going to tell
me what you're going on about?

132
00:08:16,817 --> 00:08:17,858
[NARIHISAGO]
I don't know about you,

133
00:08:17,942 --> 00:08:20,400
but I'm done with the chit-chat!

134
00:08:25,067 --> 00:08:29,608
[NARIHISAGO groaning]

135
00:08:29,692 --> 00:08:31,733
[NARIHISAGO]
You won't make me scream.

136
00:08:31,817 --> 00:08:33,900
You and I are just
getting started.

137
00:08:33,983 --> 00:08:36,358
Are you sure you're
really a police officer?

138
00:08:36,442 --> 00:08:38,442
You fight like a child.

139
00:08:44,983 --> 00:08:47,483
[chuckles]

140
00:08:51,650 --> 00:08:54,567
What happened to fighting
fair and square, like a man?

141
00:08:54,650 --> 00:08:56,817
I said we'd fight your
way, and we are.

142
00:08:56,900 --> 00:08:59,650
Only this time, you're the one
who was caught by surprise.

143
00:08:59,733 --> 00:09:00,900
Dammit!

144
00:09:19,650 --> 00:09:23,317
Good. You've still got
some fight in you.

145
00:09:28,192 --> 00:09:31,067
