158
00:10:38,400 --> 00:10:40,858
Don't die on me. I'll get help.

159
00:10:40,942 --> 00:10:43,233
[NARIHISAGO]
Momoki.

160
00:10:43,317 --> 00:10:45,108
Stairs behind the curtain...

161
00:10:45,192 --> 00:10:47,525
There's a victim
still down there.

162
00:10:49,108 --> 00:10:54,067
[music playing]

163
00:11:02,900 --> 00:11:03,983
Damn!

164
00:11:04,067 --> 00:11:06,275
You're safe!
I'm with the police!

165
00:11:10,442 --> 00:11:11,983
[MOMOKI]
You poor thing.

166
00:11:12,067 --> 00:11:15,650
If you can hear me,
tell me your name.

167
00:11:16,817 --> 00:11:19,983
Help's on the way. Hold on.

168
00:11:20,067 --> 00:11:22,817
[GIRL]
My name's Asukai.

169
00:11:23,858 --> 00:11:28,733
My name's Kiki... Asukai.

170
00:11:28,817 --> 00:11:32,942
