171
00:11:44,692 --> 00:11:46,483
[NARIHISAGO]
Can't be her.

172
00:11:46,567 --> 00:11:48,358
Look at this.

173
00:11:51,358 --> 00:11:52,442
[KIKI ASUKAI]
Who is it?

174
00:11:52,525 --> 00:11:54,483
[NARIHISAGO]
Detective Akihito Narihisago

175
00:11:54,567 --> 00:11:57,067
with the First
Investigative Division.

176
00:11:57,150 --> 00:11:59,025
You can come in.

177
00:12:03,025 --> 00:12:06,733
Looks like the firework
festival's happening tonight.

178
00:12:09,608 --> 00:12:11,733
You're Kaeru.

179
00:12:13,275 --> 00:12:18,275
What are you?
Part of the Mizuhanome?

180
00:12:18,358 --> 00:12:20,858
And what is a Mizuhanome?

181
00:12:20,942 --> 00:12:23,233
[NARIHISAGO]
Never mind. Sorry for intruding.

182
00:12:23,317 --> 00:12:27,525
It's nice to meet you,
Miss Kiki Asukai.

183
00:12:27,608 --> 00:12:30,650
[KIKI ASUKAI] That man with
the gray hair, where is he?

184
00:12:30,733 --> 00:12:32,483
You mean the Challenger?

185
00:12:32,567 --> 00:12:38,483
"Challenger"? So... that's
what people were calling him.

186
00:12:38,567 --> 00:12:42,650
[CHALLENGER] I want you to
hit me as hard as you can.

187
00:12:42,733 --> 00:12:46,150
You understand? This isn't
part of your dreams anymore.

188
00:12:46,233 --> 00:12:49,608
If you don't fight back this
time, you'll actually die.

189
00:12:49,692 --> 00:12:51,317
Die already!

190
00:12:53,192 --> 00:12:56,192
